    "\n",
    "## Multivariate normal\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "f(\\bf{x}) = \\det{(2\\pi\\Sigma)}^{-1/2} \\exp{\\left(-\\frac{1}{2} (\\bf{x}-\\mu)^T \\Sigma^{-1}(\\bf{x}-\\mu) \\right)}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.small}"
   ]
